# vox-privacy-audit allow-list
#
# Each non-empty, non-comment line is a substring. If a finding line from
# scripts/audit.sh contains that substring, the finding is suppressed.
#
# Be specific. Allow file:line or a qualified class name, not a bare keyword.
# Every entry should have a comment above it explaining why it's allowed.

